listResults.description: Welcome to your next home! A lovely 3 bedroom, 2 bath home in beautiful Lowry Heights! This condo provides lots of living space for the whole family! Entertaining is easy in your natural light-filled kitchen, with extra bar seating and a cozy breakfast nook. You'll fall in love with the master bedroom, featuring en suite full bathroom and walk-in closet! Enjoy summer days grilling out on your private patio! Ideal location for your family, with close proximity to Verbena Park, trails, and schools. Plus, quick and easy access to 225.

**Sellers will pay for 6 months of HOA Dues!**

Welcome to your next home! This lovely 2 bedroom, 2 bath condo in beautiful Denver! This condo provides lots of living space for the whole family. Entertaining is easy in your natural light-filled kitchen with extra bar seating. You'll fall in love with the master bedroom featuring en suite bathroom! Enjoy cool autumn nights on your covered patio! Ideal location for your family, with close proximity to Sunken Gardens Park. Plus, quick and easy access to Interstate 25.

Welcome to your next home! A lovely 3 bedroom, 2 bath home in beautiful Denver! This single family home provides lots of living space for the whole family, a welcoming fireplace, hardwood and carpeted floors! Entertaining is easy in your natural light-filled kitchen, with granite countertops, extra bar seating and cozy breakfast nook. Enjoy summer days grilling out on your spacious patio! Ideal location for your family, with close proximity to Kittredge Park, trails, and schools.

**Sellers will pay for 6 months of HOA Dues!**

Welcome to your next home! This lovely 1 bedroom, 1 bath condo in beautiful Denver is sure to catch your eye! This condo is just walking distance from Coors Field. Entertaining is easy in your natural light-filled kitchen, with quartz countertops and stainless steel appliances! Enjoy cool autumn nights on your balcony! Ideal location for your family, with close proximity to Commons Park and trails. Plus, quick and easy access to Interstate 25.

**Sellers will pay for 6 months of HOA Dues!**

Welcome home! This stunning loft, 1.5 bath unit is located in Denver's trendy LoHi neighborhood! Natural light pours in through large windows opening up the space. The stylish kitchen features stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, and modern open shelving. This home is in a fantastic location close to top rated restaurants like El Five, Linger, and Postino while being steps from the pedestrian bridge into downtown.  Hirshorn Park is directly across the street with space for running your puppy or shooting some hoops, and don't forget to stop by Little Man on your way home for some of the best ice cream in the city. Don't miss this rare opportunity to set down roots in one of Denver's most popular enclaves.

Back on the Market!  Buyers financing fell through.. Conventional Appraisal came back at $252k!  Beautiful 4 Bedroom 2 Bath Ranch Style Home!!!  Updated Through Out!  Featuring New Roof, New Exterior Paint, New Gutters and New Solar Panels just installed (25k value)!!  Elegant Hardwood Floors, Updated Kitchen with Granite Countertops and Subway Tile Backsplash!  Fully Finished Basement with Open Layout, 2 Bedrooms with Own Bath and Oversize Laundry Room!  Spacious Yard, Conveniently Located in the Heart of Montbello!

Check out this fully renovated 3 bed/ 2 bath home in West Barnum with open concept kitchen, brand new master suite, and detached one car garage only 10 minutes from Downtown Denver. This freshly renovated home combines the charm of an older home built in 1940 with the modern finishes and function of modern 2020 home. Enjoy the recent upgrades including brand new: windows, roof, water heater, air-conditioning unit, furnace, kitchen appliances, flooring throughout, landscaping, one car detached garage, exterior and interior paint, etc.  Hand-selected finishes create a cohesive and inviting esthetic. On the main floor, you will find a spacious open kitchen with a coveted pantry space and a large peninsula that offers plenty of seating. The kitchen flows into the dining and living space - perfect for entertaining! On the main level there are two bedrooms and a tastefully updated full bathroom. The basement with spaciously tall ceilings features a second living space, perfect for movie nights and a generously sized laundry space. The luxurious master bedroom accommodates a king size bed and is overflowing with natural light through a large egress window. The oversized closet will please even the pickiest fashionista and a tasteful en-suite with dual vanity and beautiful shower will win you over. Outdoor space abounds on this 5,862 SqFt lot. Overlook the grassy lawn from the deck right off the kitchen with space for a BBQ grill. There is also a large concrete patio for summer celebrations and brand new one car garage. This home is conveniently located near 6th Avenue Parkway, use as your route to a quick mountain escape or zip to downtown in under 10 minutes. This home is walking distance to Weir Gulch, Barnum Park, Barnum Dog Park and only minutes away from Sloan's Lake.

Beautiful house.Very clean.Totally remodeled.Tons of upgrades.Newer kitchen cabinets, ss appliances, gas range ,modern kitchen hood, granite countertops. Plenty of room to entertain.Open floor plan. Hardwood floors on main floor.Beautiful bathrooms.Basement has 2 bedrooms ,one non-conforming, family room ,laundry with washer & dryer included and updated bathroom. House is on a beautiful maintained big corner lot, with 2 sheds and a covered patio for your summer evenings.You must stop by to see it all! Sold "AS-is".

Yay!!! Showing rules being relaxed! To celebrate we are offering buyer choice for $1000 credit, can be use for closing costs, or price reduction...you name it. Front line workers get an additional $500! Landscaping done, new fence, yard work, take another look. Newly renovated home in the up and coming Westwood area. Boasts 2 bedrooms and 1 and a half baths. So fresh and so clean. The open concept New kitchen has all new stainless appliances and new cabinetry. Fresh paint inside and out, new floors, new windows and roof, new bathrooms and plumbing. New efficient electric baseboard heating. Easy access to public transportation. Shopping and plenty of restaurants nearby. Move in ready. Plenty of natural sun light. New gutters and down spouts. In opportunity zone. Lower tax rates. Great for starter or rental. No HOA.  See Virtual Tour!

Great Location in neighborhood. 3bd/2ba home (income restrictions apply) available in East GVR. Granite Counter tops in large kitchen, Master bedroom and bath. 2 car garage and gas fireplace. Backyard patio perfect for summer evening grilling. A lovely location near green space and biking path. Elevation Community Land Trust is making home ownership possible to more people. Income and other qualifications apply. We have other properties coming and encourage you to go through the online application process.

Charming 1929 Tudor bungalow on double lot with hardwoods throughout most of main level, fireplace in living room, coved ceilings, arches. Full finished basement with good height ceiling. Large front porch. This home has had the same owner for 45 years and is ready for updating throughout. 6240 lot is 1 block from the SW corner of Washington Park. Seller is unable to complete Seller's Property Disclosure. Buyer welcome to complete all needed buyer inspections but property will be sold strictly as-is.

This beautiful Victorian home is located in the desirable Sunnyside neighborhood.  Just blocks to shops, dining, parks, and entertainment in both Sunnyside and Lo-Hi.   Impeccably updated and maintained.  

The main floor features a living room with large built in entertainment center, the formal dining room with French doors that lead to the yard, the spacious kitchen, and a full bathroom with double vanity.    The second story hosts the 2 bedrooms.  The hardwood floors, tall ceilings, recessed lighting, tin ceiling, and original wood work create a warm and inviting space.

The gorgeous landscaped backyard with large deck is perfect for entertaining.   Additional features include an oversized 1 car detached garage, a covered front porch, a sprinkler system, the evaporative cooler, and additional storage in the basement.  

 -2 Bedrooms, 1 bathroom
 -1,048 finished square feet 
 -3,049 square foot lot
 -Taxes:  $1748.00 
 -Beautifully updated and maintained 
 -Excellent location

This significant Country Club home is rich in history, grand in stature and delivers an elegant lifestyle. Designed by Burnham Hoyt in the 1920's it retains much of its original character, including a 4,000 volume wood-paneled library, leaded glass windows with the initials of the original owners, a weather vane designed and gifted to the owners by Hoyt, and much more. Deemed as The Corner Chateau, this home has seen important upgrades for today's lifestyle by some of Denver's finest, BOA Construction and Canady Construction; including an open kitchen flooded with light that connects to a sitting room, family room and large private patio. This home's generous living and entertaining spaces, along with six en-suite bedrooms is further enhanced by the 17,400 sqft professionally landscaped yard and gardens, beautifully fenced for privacy. The press love this home and so will you--it's been sought out and featured time and again by local and national press. Come visit and see for yourself.

listResults.description: Don't miss out on this great home in Harvey Park.  You will love being just a few doors down from the park.   The perfectly manicured front yard and the amazing picture window give this home plenty of curb appeal.  A ton of natural light pours into the spacious living and dining rooms. The kitchen features popular white cabinetry and a cozy eat-in breakfast nook.   Picture drinking your morning coffee while gazing out at your beautiful backyard and bountiful garden with established planting beds and fruit trees.  This ranch style home includes 3 bedrooms on the main floor as well as an additional en-suite bedroom in the basement.  The finished basement includes a massive bonus room, laundry room and utility/storage area.  Use your imagination, there are so many ways to utilize this space! New roof with 5 year transferable warranty is included.  This home has 200 amps wired for the home and 60 amps wired to the 1 car attached garage.   Plenty of electricity for any future updates you may want to complete.  Harvey Park is centrally located within the Denver Metro area.  Downtown Denver, BelMar, Red Rocks are a quick drive away.

Great Location.  Income restrictions apply.  Lovely 2 story home on large lot in quiet cul de sac. Backs to green space with lots of privacy. Open floor plan with living, dining and kitchen flowing together. Large windows make it light and bright living. Large open kitchen. Family loft and three bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms. Walk in closet in spacious Master bedroom. Master bath has ample space and double sinks.  Patio is perfect for entertaining. No monthly HOA dues. Close to golf course, DIA, I70 and E470. Elevation Community Land Trust is making home ownership possible to more people. Income and other qualifications apply. We have other properties coming and encourage those that qualify to go through the online application process.

Spectacular Wellshire property on one of the best blocks in the neighborhood. This updated ranch has 3320 total square footage with 4 bedrooms and 3 baths. The spacious main floor has tons of living space with beautiful hardwood floors, crown molding and is flooded with natural light. Open floor concept with a beautiful kitchen addition, dining room, family room and living room with a brick fireplace and plantation shutters.  Main floor walks out to back yard paver patio that is charming and inviting, you will immediately want to sit down and relax in this peaceful space. There are 3 bedrooms on the main floor.  The master bedroom with a fabulous, en suite master bath is located near 2 secondary bedrooms and additional 3/4 bath. The basement offers even more space with a bedroom, bath with walk-in shower, bonus room and family room with an additional fireplace. There is space in the basement for a guest room, playroom and/or office.  The professionally landscaped 9180 square foot lot is like an oasis, perfect for all your summer entertaining. This home is updated and move in ready. Centrally located to Cherry Creek, Tech Center and close to shops and restaurants. Award winning Slavens School is just a short walk away.

listResults.description: What a location! Highland Park right down the street, walk just a few blocks to Highland Square, easy access to downtown, LoHi, Tennyson, Sloan's. Single family home with large fenced yard, updated with hardwood floors throughout, updated bathrooms. Sit out on your private back covered deck and enjoy cool Colorado evenings! Tall ceilings in this historic Denver home, large family room and great front porch.

Beautifully updated home with quick & easy access to downtown AND to the mountains. This home has just been remodeled/updated with refinished hardwood floors as you enter into the living room and dining room area.  The Kitchen has beautiful new tile flooring, new granite countertops and all new appliances.  Both bedrooms have new carpet and the entire interior of the home has been freshly painted with relaxing, modern color. The bathroom was not left out of the remodel and features a new sink & toilet, and a tub that has beautiful tile surround & gleaming glass gliding shower doors! The basement room (measures 22' 9" X 10') is great for storage and the washer and dryer hook-ups are found here. The back yard, complete with a beautiful cedar 6' fence, has a small shed (13' 6" X 9' 6"), and plenty of room to build that garage that will make this property just perfect!! The backyard is an empty canvas waiting for the new owner's creativity to make a wonderful yard space with room for a good garden! There is also room at the front of the house to create a driveway (on south side) that could possibly accommodate a couple vehicles. City living without the price you see in many other neighborhoods!  Hurry!!!!  Due to Covid-19 guidelines and restrictions, Buyer's must view the video tours of the house AND must provide a lender letter or proof of funds before seeing the home in person.

Fantastic 3 bed, 1 bath single-family home with an enormous multi-functional garage. Various creative improvements have been made, such as fiber optic internet wiring and solar panels which significantly reduce utilities and are anticipated to produce future income! The refurbished kitchen has newer appliances, including a dual fuel range with a unique drop-down cutting board affixed as the back splash. The bathroom has been completely remodeled with new tile and new vanity. Traverse the fully fenced back yard to discover the ultimate "man cave", a four-stall garage with a powerful heater, swamp cooler, and pneumatic air tool quick connects. Located close to downtown Denver in an upcoming area as evident from the new construction recently initiated. Enjoy the high walk score rating with various restaurants and shopping nearby!

Fantastic huge lot! House has a lot of potential and could easily be expanded, or scrape it and build your dream home! This is a perfect opportunity! Close to Inspiration Point Park, Lake Rhoda, Willis Case Golf Course. and quick drive to downtown and a fantastic location. Check out the area comparables! This is a cash only sale.

Showings start on May 9! We are excited to present this charming Congress Park Bungalow! Great location! Walk or ride your bike to City Park, Cheesman Park, Denver Zoo, Denver Museum of Nature & Science, Trader Joe's, Sweet Cooie's Ice Cream & Blue Pan Pizza just to name a few! This home features a covered porch, living room with wood burning fireplace surrounded by built-in cabinets. Dining room with a built-in cabinet. The Kitchen has been tastefully remodeled with stainless appliances & breakfast nook overlooking the backyard. The main level features original wood work and newly refinished hardwood floors.  The Master Suite is on the lower level complete with a newly remodeled 5 piece master bathroom, jetted tub, separate shower and double sink vanity. There is a bonus room off the Master Bedroom, perfect for a baby's room, (current use) or a dressing room / walk in closet. New carpeting installed April 2020! Laundry Room, Mechanical room, wine closet and storage located on the lower level.  The Backyard has a newly built privacy fence, large dining deck to enjoy with friends & family! 2 car garage with workbench included!

Beautiful remodeled home in prime East Wash Park! Located between the Park and Old South Gaylord Street. Filled with lots of natural light and architectural detail. This gorgeous home blends original charm with modern updates and one of a kind living. Prof finished backyard paradise is perfect for entertaining, gardening, or relaxing with outdoor kitchen, gas fireplace, stone patio, mature trees and lush landscaping. Gorgeous kitchen with slab granite, high end appliances, bar, wine fridge and formal dining. Huge family room features vaulted ceilings, built ins and gas fireplace. Retreat to large upstairs master with sitting area and marble/tile bathroom. Spacious finished family room in basement, bedroom, full bath, laundry room and large finished bonus room for exercise or storage. *This home offers the best in Wash Park Living!

Super chic Victorian around the corner from all of RiNo's coolest restaurants, bars and coffee shops. Refinished original Brazilian Cherry floors in the living area. Open floor plan with tall ceilings throughout. Bright bedrooms with custom Elfa closets. En suite master bathroom and huge master closet! SchoolHouse light fixtures throughout. Design wallpaper in the uber cute power bath. Hip kitchen with butcher block countertops. Backyard is perfect for summer BBQ's. Electric gate in the back yard with remote so it's easy to pull into the backyard for off street parking. Zoned for garage or ADU. New sewer line and roof in 2017.

This 5 Bedroom, 3 Bathroom home has a little something for everyone. Upon entering, you will be greeted by the living room with vaulted ceilings, abundance of light and plenty of room. The hardwood floors will lead you into two of the three bedrooms in the main level with a full bathroom placed in between the two bedrooms. The master bedroom with full ensuite bathroom also has vaulted ceilings and is large enough to easily fit a king sized bed. One of the biggest wow moments you will have will be when you enter into the white and bright recently remodeled kitchen. Cooking delicious home cooked meals will be a joy to create with a gas stove, a bounty of countertop space and storage.  Speaking of storage, this house has so much storage peppered around the entire house and a shed in the backyard. The tucked away staircase takes you to both the attached garage and fully finished basement. The basement holds two additional bedrooms with egress windows, a rec room and a ¾ bathroom and laundry room. The large lot not only gives you some breathing room from your neighbors but also provides plenty of off street parking, a large backyard and side yard. This home truly has it all, space, light, storage and of character do not miss out!

Great looking paired home in The Vistas with a 2 car garage and a finished basement adding a fourth bedroom. Shows fantastic, owners have taken great pride. This one will be taken fast, so please do not wait to schedule a private tour TODAY! Home is located within minutes from restaurants and shopping centers.

NEW PRICE!! Lovely 4 bedroom, 2 bathroom ranch in University Hills - by far the lowest price per square foot in the neighborhood! Upon entering home you'll find an open floor plan with abundant natural lighting. Living room with hardwood floors & pellet stove leads into the home addition with dining room and open kitchen. Updated kitchen boasts quartz countertops, stainless steel appliances and kitchen island. Bonus office space. Separate laundry room with sink and ample cabinet storage. 4 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms are privately situated. New paint throughout, new exterior doors, new dishwasher and newer furnace. Professional landscaping in the front yard and fenced-in backyard. Amazing location with a short walk to the Light Rail & High Line Canal Trail and easy access to I-25. You don't want to miss this great opportunity to live in Denver. There is a 3D virtual tour for this property - don't forget to check it out!

Come enjoy the best of Zuni Park!! Turn-key ready home with 4 bedroom 2 FULL baths and hardwood flooring upstairs. Full Basement with family room and two bedrooms. See Pics for Layout. Front porch for watching the sun set, and a patio in the private backyard for entertaining. Enclosed fence for your furry friends! Both front and backyards have sprinklers. New high efficiency furnace and HUGE A/C unit. Roof is only 3 years old. Driveway for two cars AND a detached Two Car Alley Garage. Recent remodel. Close to all the Tennyson shops and coffee shops. Easy access to downtown and to the Mountains.

Wow! Must See. Brand new. Modern living at an AMAZING price. Bright open floor plan with lots of natural light. Large kitchen with granite countertops and stainless steel appliances. Vaulted ceilings in the living area and Luxury vinyl plank floors throughout the downstairs. There is a second-floor laundry room which includes a new front-load washer & dryer. Large master bedroom with plenty of closet space. Attached 2-car garage. Everything is new, just move in! Amenities include the clubhouse, pool, dog park, pollinator park, and a future Denver Public Park! This home is offered through Elevation Community Land Trust (ECLT). ECLT makes homeownership possible for Colorado families through a land trust model, a proven tool for creating and preserving accessible, inclusive communities for generations. Income and other qualifications apply.

SUPER-HIP CONTEMPORARY REMODEL (In-Person Showings Permitted Starting 5/8/20)  GORGEOUS UPDATES: The original hardwood floors throughout main and upper floor have been carefully refinished in a modern gray tone. Other design features include: white shaker cabinets, soft grey quartz countertops, matte black hardware and fixtures, single-panel doors. Fantastic bay windows with built-in window seats are perfect for reading a book or drinking a cup of coffee.  GREAT OPEN FLOORPLAN: the large open concept main floor is perfect for entertaining with huge kitchen island...this home feels even bigger than measured SF. The upstairs has a guest bedroom, a full bathroom with a cool mid-century square bathtub, as well as a generous master suite with double sinks, spa like shower and two closets (including walk-in). The lower level has another guest bedroom/office, third bathroom and a cozy family room with a gas fireplace and access to the backyard. The big covered back patio is a great space to spend a summer evening enjoying a cool beverage. Hot water baseboard heating creates a very even heat and separate central AC will take care of you all summer long.  AWESOME LOCATION: Just one block to Rocky Mountain Lake park and walking distance to groceries, shops and restaurants on Tennyson with easy access to downtown and I-70. Act quick this home will be gone before you know it!

Investors welcome. Fixer uppers welcome. Home being sold AS-IS. Zoned I-A light industrial. Can convert to commercial to house a business.  Live/Work opportunity. Fix and rent for investment.  CAN CONSTRUCT AN AUXILIARY BUILDING WITH GARAGE AND APARTMENT ON TOP TO GENERATE INCOME check with Denver Planning/Zone to verify and confirm uses

If you are looking for a cozy, meticulously cared-for bungalow in Alamo Placita, you have found it. From the gleaming oak floors to the built-in bookcases to the ornate radiators to the antique oven in the kitchen, this home harkens back to a less complicated world. Yet, it brings with it a newer, energy efficient boiler, a tankless water heater, a newer roof, storm windows, and garage doors. The front porch provides ample room for sitting to watch a sunset or chatting with neighbors passing by. The double lot offers plenty of space for gardening and entertaining in the backyard. This is more than a house. It's home. And the location couldn't be better.  A block to the hiking/biking path along Cherry Creek to downtown or to the mall. Alamo Placita Park is 2 blocks away and Wash Park is a short jog or bike ride.  It's 3 blocks to the shops and restaurants on 6th Ave, from Safeway for groceries to Pablos for coffee, and just up the street is Byblos Cafe. Come and look. You'll be pleased to make an offer.

Architectural Digest-worthy 7,957 square foot luxury single-family residence, located on the most desirable corner lot in Cherry Creek North. Privately commissioned in 2016, this home embodies the very finest in modern luxury and quality construction rarely seen in Denver.   No expense has been spared in this concrete-constructed work of art. Bulthaup kitchen, Bulthaup designed His and Her walk-in closets with custom cabinetry imported from Italy, Waterworks bathrooms, radiant heat throughout, white oak floors, top-of-the-line Smart House technology, motorized designer blinds, elevator, commercial-grade windows, two-story master bedroom suite with spiral staircase to a third floor private retreat with outdoor patio.   Incomparable expansive courtyard, surrounded by NanaWall sliding glass walls that create seamless indoor/outdoor entertaining. For the most discriminating Buyer, 395 Detroit is a true oasis offering supreme privacy, a premier locale and convenient access to the finest shopping and dining.

Centrally located home, minutes from downtown - Easy access to shops, highways, downtown, restaurants Lots of offstreet parking, carpot, large yard, two ful bathrooms, cozy and cute house near 6th Avenue newer roof, newer paint, updated bathrooms, updated kitchen. Call for a private showing.

Please don't blink or you will miss this Mid-Mod Nod! Your home has been completely updated wall to wall! Cross the threshold through your custom 6 light Douglas Fir entry door. The large windows and french doors evenly illuminate this elegant space. The design team thought through every detail so you can move right in and enjoy this high-end transformation! Stroll through the double barn doors to your exquisite master suite including an exposed brick wall. The master bath features floor to ceiling custom finishes that include frameless euro glass, mosaic tile accents, a floating vanity with quartz top along with mid modern "coffin" floor tile. This home has all the updates you have been searching for! Custom designed cabinets to include soft close doors and drawers, Kohler fixtures and state of the art Samsung appliances. Saunter outside to your covered patio and spacious back yard ready for your own personal touches. Load up the moving truck because this house will make an amazing home! New 6 foot privacy fence will be installed prior to closing. Images are just a sneak peek of this modern space! Professional pictures uploaded Wednesday.

This charming home is a beautiful blend of historic charm and craftsmanship that stands the test of time. It is centrally located in the trendy City Park South neighborhood. You are within walking distance to restaurants, entertainment, City Park, Sprouts, Denver Museum of Nature and Science and the zoo. Upon entering, you are greeted by a beautiful bright and sunny living room adjacent to the large dining room that features a window seat overlooking the lovely back garden. Also on the main floor is a bedroom with a walk-in closet, full bathroom, enclosed sunroom and a kitchen with an abundance of cabinets and stainless steel appliances. The word work on the second level is stunning. The large master bedroom features two walk-in closets with built-ins. There is a bonus room that could be used as a craft room or study. The secondary bedroom has a ceiling fan and two closets. The remodeled bathroom includes new vanity, granite and tile. The basement has a finished room with a closet, laundry area with utility sink and has plenty of room for future expansion. It also has a private entrance. The backyard is great for entertaining with a patio area, nice landscaping, two car detached garage and additional alley parking. Don't miss out on this fabulous City Park home in such an unbeatable location!

CALLING ALL INVESTORS!  Sitting in the heart of the Highlands, this home is PERFECT for a fix and flip or income property!  Interior has good bones, lots of potential for making this a true gem! Room in basement to add a bed and bath with its own entrance to get full market value! Newer furnace, AC and hot water heater. Exterior needs a little love. 1 block from retail, restaurants and local hangouts, and only 5 blocks from Historic Highlands Square.  2-car garage and plenty of off-street parking. Bring your highest and best offer! A must-see, you will not be disappointed!!

Beautiful Washington Park bungalow on large lot. Main level boasts an open living/dining area with gas fireplace and adorable kitchen with granite countertops, gas stove and stainless steel appliances. Beautiful patio area off dining room with Pergola. Finished basement has one non-conforming bedroom, laundry. Close to Wash Park, South Pearl Street and close proximity to the light rail. Live well now with a land investment ample enough for a future dream house.

listResults.address: 9255 E Lehigh Ave APT 227, Denver, CO 80237
listResults.description: Beautifully updated 2 bedroom townhome very close to shopping, restaurants, I-225 and I-25.  Brand new stainless steel LG appliances including washer and dryer.  Easy to show.  Near light rail access at Dayton Station and Cherry Creek Canal.  Possession on day of closing.

You'll love this fantastic two-story home that is located in the active community of Green Valley Ranch. Immediately upon entering you are taken away by the flowing floorplan that boasts fresh interior paint through out in a chic grey color scheme. A spacious living flows easily into the dining room and kitchen for easy entertaining. The stunning kitchen features granite countertops, cherry cabinetry, pantry and stainless steel appliances. Upstairs, flexible loft space makes a great family room, playroom or office. Spacious master with tray ceilings and a luxurious 5-piece bath is sure to become a personal oasis. 2 additional bedrooms and a full bathroom complete the upstairs of this beautiful home. Enjoy Colorado's 360 days of sunshine in your private backyard with large garden beds,prefect for your organic flower or vegetable garden. Enjoy being just a short distance to local shopping and dining, and easy access to highways; just 20 minutes from downtown Denver and only 10 minutes to DIA. Green Valley Ranch offers a community pool and year round events including a farmers market and live concerts at the GVR amphitheater!

Opportunity awaits at this 1958 ranch home on a large corner lot in a quiet, tree-lined neighborhood. Sunny main floor hosts a wood-burning fireplace, 3/4 bathroom, and 3 bedrooms, 2 of which are connected via a 1/2 Jack and Jill bath. Finished basement with another wood-burning fireplace and Jack and Jill bath is a full footprint of the home and adds excellent additional living and storage space. Recent updates include a new roof in December of 2019 and a new hot water tank in 2018. The over-sized attached 2-car garage is connected via a covered walkway to the front door. Generous fenced backyard has a storage shed, patio, and deck and awaits personalization from your green thumb. Excellent location on a secluded street in an established neighborhood close to schools, parks, and trails. Quick access to shopping, dining, Sante Fe, Federal Blvd & RTD make for painless commuting. The possibilities and potential are limited only by your imagination!
